}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This device identifies as 4 separate USB devices - two w/ 2109:0810 IDs (USB 3.0, only visible with an xHCI controller) and two w/ 2109:3431 IDs (USB 2.0).
The power adapter included with the device appears to be a '''Powertron Electronics''' PA1045-2HI (100-240VAC [50~60Hz] 1.0A -> 12VDC 3.0A).
